OL,3,CPhil Taylor urges Luke Littler to 'put
OL,4,Cthat phone down'
OL,6,FFormer darts world champion Phil
OL,7,FTaylor has told Luke Littler to "put
OL,8,Fthat phone down" in order to curb the
OL,9,Fbooing crowds.
OL,11,FThe 19-year-old has been booed during
OL,12,Fhis last two Premier League outings
OL,13,Fafter his spat with Gian van Veen in
OL,14,FManchester three weeks ago. He next
OL,15,Ftakes to the oche in Liverpool on
OL,16,FThursday, 23 April.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@PO]
