PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776957068
OL,3,CPhil Taylor urges Luke Littler to 'put
OL,4,Cthat phone down'
OL,6,FBut Taylor believes Littler's social
OL,7,Fmedia presence is baiting fans further
OL,8,Fand says the player from Warrington
OL,9,Fshould head to the practice room
OL,10,Finstead.
OL,12,F"He needs to get off social media `
OL,13,Fput that phone down and just don't
OL,14,Fkeep posting things as a reaction",
OL,15,FPhil told the Double Tops podcast.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776957068
OL,3,CPhil Taylor urges Luke Littler to 'put
OL,4,Cthat phone down'
OL,6,F"I have social media, but I have
OL,7,Fpeople to post for me. I was always
OL,8,Ftold, 'whatever you do, don't have an
OL,9,Fopinion on social media'. What I'm
OL,10,Ftrying to say is you can't win on
OL,11,Fthere, so don't try to.
OL,13,F"He needs to practise more; he
OL,14,Fliterally does not practise. We did an
OL,15,Fexhibition together. I was there as
OL,16,Fthe guest speaker and Luke sat there
OL,17,Ffor about two and a half hours on his
OL,18,Fphone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776957068
OL,3,CPhil Taylor urges Luke Littler to 'put
OL,4,Cthat phone down'
OL,6,F"He was playing Luke Humphries, who
OL,7,Fwas practising like mad for it, but he
OL,8,Fwas there just playing on his phone.
OL,10,F"I asked him if he was going to
OL,11,Fpractise and he went, 'nah'. He then
OL,12,Fgoes and beats Humphries 8-1!
OL,14,F"I was thinking, 'this is
OL,15,Fimpossible'...but he did it. For Luke
OL,16,Fto do what he's doing with so little
OL,17,Fpractice shows the amount of talent
OL,18,Fhe's got."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
