FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776957068
OL,3,CPhil Taylor urges Luke Littler to 'put
OL,4,Cthat phone down'
OL,6,FTaylor reckons Littler's form has
OL,7,Fdropped since his fall-out with the
OL,8,FDutchman and he puts that down to the
OL,9,Fcrowd reaction.
OL,11,F"It does seem to have had an impact
OL,12,Fbecause he isn't playing as well," he
OL,13,Fadded. "Eventually it will stop but I
OL,14,Fthink, at the moment, the thing I'd
OL,15,Fsay to Luke is just go and play out of
OL,16,Fyour skin.
OL,18,F"If you do that, the crowd will turn
OL,19,Fand be back on your side."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@bO]uD@HOUzD@AOU{D@ZO]
